	* src/Makefile.am: Remove libpthread and
	Update accordingly.
	* src/ath.c, src/ath.h (ath_mutex_init)
	(ath_mutex_destroy, ath_mutex_lock, ath_mutex_unlock): Removed.
	* src/ath.h (ATH_MUTEX_INITIALIZER): Removed.
