	* lang/python/pyme/core.py (Core.get_key): Return public keys by
	default, improve docstring.
	* lang/python/examples/testCMSgetkey.py: Update example.
	* lang/python/examples/verifydetails.py: Likewise.

	GnuPG-bug-id: 2751

