	Rework status table to be less dynamically generated.
	* src/Makefile.am (EXTRA_DIST): Remove mkstatus.
	(BUILT_SOURCE, MOSTLYCLEANFILES): Remove.
	(main_sources): Remove status-table.h, extra-stati.h.
